value: India south of the Himalayas to w Myanmar

Of local occurrence in India and Burma as follows: Garhwal and Sikkim; Bengal south of the Godavery and west to Wyne Gunga; Seoni in the Central Provinces; southwestern India from the Wynaad to Travancore; Cachar and Sylhet.
refer: Peter's Checklist of the Birds of the World
